Apakah kamu mengerti?

118
00:07:37,239 --> 00:07:38,458
Tidak sama sekali.

119
00:08:37,125 --> 00:08:38,605
Anne, halo.

120
00:08:39,649 --> 00:08:40,781
Bagaimana tadi?

121
