meringkasnya untuk aku.

147
00:09:47,891 --> 00:09:49,153
Ye... ya, Pak.

148
00:09:52,635 --> 00:09:57,684
Seberapa pendek kamu
lebih suka ringkasan ini?

149
00:10:00,034 --> 00:10:01,818
Empat kalimat atau kurang.

150
00:10:03,167 --> 00:10:05,779
