174
00:11:38,393 --> 00:11:40,090
Luwak yang bisa bicara.

175
00:11:40,221 --> 00:11:41,265
Ya.

176
00:11:41,788 --> 00:11:43,659
Makhluk itu, yang bernama Gef,

